              double defense,

              com.googlecode.lanterna.TextCharacter sprite,
              java.lang.String name,
              Maze map)
        Constructor for the abstract entity object: an entity is able to move around and interact with its environment.
        Parameters:
        x - The x-coordinate of this entity.
        y - The y-coordinate of this entity.
        hp - The health that this entity has.
        damage - The damage that this entity deals.
        defense - The percentage of damage that this entity recieves from enemies.
        accuracy - The percent chance that this entity lands a hit.
        sprite - The char that represents the entity on the playfield.
        name - The name of this entity.
        map - The map that this entity belongs to.
